    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a green colorant that is a mixture of cadmium yellow with chromium oxide (viridian), or a mixture of cadmium yellow and phthalocyanine green.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047822/MFA Conservation and Art Material Encyclopedia Online: CAMEO (2005-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指一種綠色著色劑，為鎘黃與氧化鉻（銘綠）的混合物，或鎘黃和酞菁綠之混合物。 </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
